# TL_SM: Transfer Learning in Surrogate Modeling

A repository implementing transfer learning techniques for surrogate modeling applications.

## Overview

This project explores the application of transfer learning methods to surrogate modeling, enabling efficient knowledge transfer between related modeling tasks and reducing the computational cost of training surrogate models from scratch.

## Features

- Transfer learning implementations for surrogate models
- Pre-trained model support for faster convergence
- Adaptable architectures for different problem domains
- Performance benchmarking utilities

## Installation

```bash
# Clone the repository
git clone https://github.com/avionat/tl_sm.git
cd tl_sm

# Install the module
pip install git+https://github.com/avionat/tl_sm
OR use your cloned repository
```
# Install dependencies (included in setup.py)
```

